name: Anthony
message: We've ordered a lot from the McDonald's in the area over the last few years, and they've gotten our order right and to us quickly more times than I can count. Men, keep your women happy and give them McDonald's when they're feeling down. It's just the right thing to do!

name: Frankie
message: There seems to be a disconnect between doordash and the actual establishment whereby I get charged more than I should because items are missing.

name: Francesca
message: Missing extra patty on burger happy meal
